                <h1>Fritz Mayer, founder of POLIS and Ph.D. in public policy, is leaving Duke for Denver</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/8b17b935-266d-4525-b5f7-cb52a464d173.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            

